sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant ActivityController
    participant PostActivityUseCase
    participant ActivityService
    participant Repository

    Client->>ActivityController: POST /activities
    ActivityController->>PostActivityUseCase: execute(request)
    PostActivityUseCase->>ActivityService: postActivity(request)
    ActivityService->>Repository: save(activity)
    Repository-->>ActivityService: activity
    ActivityService-->>PostActivityUseCase: activity
    PostActivityUseCase-->>ActivityController: activity
    ActivityController-->>Client: ResponseEntity(activity)
    